"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"When we’re creating a habit — say, meditation or practicing a language — we often try to encourage ourselves by creating an unbroken streak.\\n\\n100 straight days of meditation! 30 straight days of practicing Chinese!\\n\\nThese are amazing accomplishments, and we should let ourselves feel encouraged when we have consistency like this.\\n\\nHowever, what happens when the streak is broken? When the streak goes down to a Big Zero?\\n\\nThis can be incredibly discouraging, and we then often want to give up.\\n\\nHowever, even more powerful than the consistency of a streak is what I call **Practicing with Zero**.\",\"timestamp\":1637735519,\"title\":\"Practicing with Zero\"},\"digest\":\"nTn6Gu9aB9pNNVrqDbL25sdJp4yhW1CiGW2EWDsAqkA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF619c015C99c1BbCBF394997e28dB004EFa82067\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"lvU4TDkvtgV1Dm-jUIrd3FBiUqiAfjCwM-YTfH9g5gs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"htIC-UHqDXRHsin9zs3QHteZgahy6QP7giJvo-Tj8U8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"djKGCfz_38kYIrT9_P-2PFl5Vc-QpAqsZ_5Z9RJbAtShueB6B8-xP9hd6R_5qG3FvwTKVnbm3DX7v8MFrHFmbw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xf3ebefabfed8f574c6cf2ee86cd4df8e78e396a707683355221d5f5915e4faab54865570221fdfab819201f0ed05bfcab290c0add7acaecc4436a9302c86f82a1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"lvU4TDkvtgV1Dm-jUIrd3FBiUqiAfjCwM-YTfH9g5gs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"htIC-UHqDXRHsin9zs3QHteZgahy6QP7giJvo-Tj8U8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"nTn6Gu9aB9pNNVrqDbL25sdJp4yhW1CiGW2EWDsAqkA\"}"